Package structure.grid

Provides classes for creating and working with Grid object.

          Description

Class Summary
AtomGrid Class for creating and handling grid objects for atom coordinates.
Grid Class for handling general grid objects.
GridCell  
GridUtilities Class to create and handle grid objects for AtomList objects.
Path Class that stores a list of GridCells objects as a Path object.
 

Enum Summary
GridCell.Value Value enumerator which determines which type values an object can be assigned, primarily for GridCell objects.
